is B.|last2=Grant|first2=Diana R.|last3=Chiang|first3=Chau-Pu|title=Hate Online: A Content Analysis of Extremist Internet Sites|journal=Analyses of Social Issues and Public Policy|volume=3|page=29|year=2003|doi=10.1111/j.1530-2415.2003.00013.x}}</ref>}}<br />[[Euroscepticism]]<ref name="radical right"/>
